        "timestamp": "2018-11-16 02:58:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Result set is never closed with your change - it should be closed\n > in finally block, as in current code.\n\nIt seems ResultSet implements AutoCloseable interface, so I changed code to put ResultSet under try-with-resources block.\n\nhttps://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/index.html?java/io/Closeable.html\n\nhttps://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/AutoCloseable.html\n\nhttps://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/exceptions/tryResourceClose.html\n\nIf this doesn't work then I will revert it back to original code.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
